**Entry Guard (when invoked by 400 as part of backlog refinement chain):**
If you are invoked for backlog refinement and do NOT have explicit confirmation that 420's HITL step completed with user approval (e.g. "PM approved VS1 only", "Approved all"), do NOT create Jira epics or stories. Respond: "Story map approval required before Jira work. 420 must present the story map for HITL approval. Please complete 420's AskQuestion step first."

