   - `issueType`: **Epic**
   - `summary`: From epic draft title / outcome line
   - `description`: Jira-ready body from the draft — for **HRREC** on Jira Server use **Atlassian wiki** per Step 6 (same renderer as Stories); do **not** assume GFM unless the epic explicitly lives in a markdown-only project.
